---
title: Lemony Pan-Seared Chicken with Pesto, Peas, and Potatoes
description: This recipe features a side dish built around the four Ps: pesto, peas, potatoes, and pine nuts (and a bonus fifth if you count seasoning with pepper). Pesto brings those big herby flavors, while peas add a pop of spring green. Potatoes are the good ol’ comforting standby, and pine nuts have that satisfying crunch. Top with a lemon-drizzled chicken breast and call it perfection on a plate.
